India's state owned &lt;National ThermalPower Corp Ltd> signed a 169.1 mln mark Italian buyer's credit,Bankers Trust Co, a joint lead manager, said.    The 15-1/2 year facility, with a six year grace period,carries fixed interest of 6.48 pct. It is guaranteed by theIndian government with an interest subsidy provided by Italy'sexport credit agency, Mediocredito Centrale.    The lead managers are the State Bank of India, GrindlaysBank Plc and MecFint (Jersey) Ltd. Managers are Dresdner (SouthEast Asia) Ltd, Mitsui Trust and Banking Co Ltd and the UCOBank. Co-manager is DB Asia Finance (HK) Ltd. REUTER&#3;